                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";'>Join {{url('/')}} as we launch a unique bridal network powered by powerful tech, supported by an agency of digital marketing experts and led by a team of wedding industry experts who live and breath lead generation for the wedding industry. {{url('/')}} is poised to become THE destination for Toronto couples.</span></p>
