                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";'>Beyond pretty storefronts, the goal is to get you more than just names to follow up on endlessly and manually. My Health Squad turns your profile into a marketing automation portal by including CRM tools unprecedented in any dashboard in the industry. Your dashboard includes LeadGen Pro which allows you to create workflows, nurture campaigns and drip email programs.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";'>Membership Levels and Pricing</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";'>Free &ndash; List your business with no obligation. You will have the opportunity to claim your leads as they come in and upgrade to take advantage of Pro tools when the time is right for you. Click here to get started.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";'>Premium &ndash; Guaranteed positions above Free Listings. Includes LeadGen Pro for managing internal leads as well as access to a-la-carte marketing opportunities. Click here to build your package.</span></p>
                                       <p style='margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style='font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";'>Push &ndash; Guaranteed positions above Premium and Free. Includes LeadGen Pro for managing internal AND external leads (Facebook, Instagram, Google, your website). Four Newsletter Sponsorships are included in your membership as well as access to other a-la-carte push marketing opportunities. Click here to build your package.</span></p>
